mdException.name: net.geoprism.registry.etl.export.dhis2.MultipleLevelOneOrgUnitException
mdException.message: This Organisation Unit cannot be created in DHIS2 because it would create multiple Organisation Units at level 1. DHIS2 only supports one level one Organisation Unit.

mdException.name: net.geoprism.registry.etl.export.dhis2.ParentExternalIdException
mdException.message: This Geo-Object cannot be exported because it contains a parent [{parentLabel}] which does not have an external id. Parents must exist in DHIS2 unless the Geo-Object is exported at level 1.

mdException.name: net.geoprism.registry.etl.export.dhis2.NoParentException
mdException.message: Could not find a parent at SyncLevel [{syncLevel}] of Geo-Object Type [{typeCode}] in hierarchy [{hierarchyCode}] at date [{dateLabel}]
